Package: linearregression
Type: Package
Title: construct linear regression model
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiwen Feng
Maintainer: Xiwen Feng <xiwenf@umich.edu> 
Description: Mimic existing R functions for linear regression and ANOVA. Compute leverage values and three commonly used resisuals (standardized, internally studentized, and externally studentized residuals), as well as diagnostic statistics for identifying outliers (DFFITS, Cook's Distance, and COVRATIO) with their respective plotting functions.  
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Depends:
    stats,
    tidyr,
    ggplot2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    car,
    ggbeeswarm,
    covr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
